    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the hotlines. i've looked. but those people just say the same scripted things, and it doesn't actually fix the emptiness. it's like, everyone is telling me to keep \"fighting\" but what am i even fighting for? it's just more work and more stress. if i could just stop existing, the pressure would finally be gone. wouldn't that be a more peaceful solution than just constantly struggling?",
